${h}${h} Data product overview

This repository is the **instantiated data product** created from the **GCP PostgreSQL â†’ BigQuery ingest** blueprint. It implements a governed pipeline: **read-only PostgreSQL** extraction (one **input port** per configured schema), **your** transformation in **`application/transform_hook.py`**, **JSON Schema** validation against the **output port** contract, and **dlt** load into **BigQuery** with **GCS** staging.

